dn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe.jpg\" alt=\"Mary Berry Set of 4 Green Pasta Bowls\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5a6FTXtuocZ29nvdGCrCYe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMary Berry At Home\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMary Berry Set of 4 Green Pasta Bowls\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eMary is one of \u003cem\u003eIdeal Home\u0026#39;s \u003c/em\u003emost celebrated alumni, so it felt fitting to ask her about how involved she was in the creative process behind her tableware collections.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;It started with my Signature range – a simple classic design, which is timeless, and shows off the food so well,\u0026#39; Mary begins. \u0026#39;One of my new tableware collections, Botanical, features elegant ferns decorating fine china without detracting for the food.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eShe goes onto say \u0026#39;I’m immensely proud of it. I’ve been involved from the start, throughout the stages of design.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf.jpg\" alt=\"Mary Berry\u0026#39;s at home tableware collection\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/zqyfStGKdyoc9wXD3qtbnf.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Mary Berry At Home/PR Direct)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith such longevity working in food preparation and styling, I guessed that Mary must have seen plenty of tableware trends come and go. So does she feel like the emphasis on functional tableware rather than just pretty pieces has full circle?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-CUTdJsgLRthrtxAadckMBZ\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#39;I feel they can be both,\u0026#39; says Mary. \u0026#39;As both my ranges are functional, whilst also being attractive (without being overpowering). I like the food to stand out, and for my Signature collection, the design is subtle but elegant.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5.jpg\" alt=\"Mary Berry at home tableware collection\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/B8bx5xULYU3ghRaQRfxiS5.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: NEXT)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAs for her new collection, \u0026#39;The At Home tableware range is vibrant yet modern and can be displayed decoratively in your kitchen.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eJust as when she was responsible for \u003cem\u003eIdeal Home\u0026#39;s \u003c/em\u003efood pages, it\u0026#39;s clear that there\u0026#39;s no cutting corners with Mary\u0026#39;s output. \u0026#39;Quality is so important\u0026#39; she says. \u0026#39;And ensuring attention to detail. For example, the handles have to feel right when held and the lids need to fit perfectly.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD.jpg\" alt=\"Mary Berry\u0026#39;s At Home collection\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/cK9po8FQFKK3zTSA3dDiFD.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: NEXT)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eFrom the looks of the collection, the emphasis on high-standards is definitely there. I for one am eyeing up the pasta bowls to make it feel like I\u0026#39;m on Mediterranean shores this summer!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
